{
    "id": "48097b56-d09e-4d0c-9c18-a103219503aa",
    "title": "hs",
    "content": "<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd\">\n<html><head><meta name=\"qrichtext\" content=\"1\" /><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /><style type=\"text/css\">\np, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }\nhr { height: 1px; border-width: 0; }\nli.unchecked::marker { content: \"\\2610\"; }\nli.checked::marker { content: \"\\2612\"; }\n</style></head><body style=\" font-family:'Inter','Segoe UI','sans-serif'; font-size:9pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;\">\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">\ud83c\udf0d\u2728 </span><span style=\" font-size:12pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">Why Did Allah Create This World And Humans?</span><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\"> \u2728</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">IMAM, this is one of the biggest questions a human can ask \ud83e\udd0d<br />Let\u2019s understand it in very simple words.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">\ud83c\udf1f </span><span style=\" font-size:12pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">1\ufe0f\u20e3 To Worship Him</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">In the </span><span style=\" font-size:12pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">Qur'an</span><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">, Allah says:</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:40px; margin-right:40px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">\u201cI did not create jinn and humans except to worship Me.\u201d</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">But worship does NOT mean only prayer.</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">Worship means:</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1; padding-left: 18px\">\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Knowing Allah</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Loving Him</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Obeying Him</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Living with honesty and justice</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Doing good</li></ul>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">So the main purpose is:<br />\ud83d\udc49 To recognize our Creator and live according to His guidance.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">\ud83e\udde0 </span><span style=\" font-size:12pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">2\ufe0f\u20e3 To Test Us</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">Allah created life as a test.</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">Not a school test with paper \u2014<br />But a life test:</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1; padding-left: 18px\">\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Will we choose good or bad?</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Will we be patient?</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Will we be grateful?</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Will we be fair?</li></ul>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">Without this world, there is no test.<br />Without test, no reward or punishment.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">\ud83d\udc8e </span><span style=\" font-size:12pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">3\ufe0f\u20e3 To Show His Names And Attributes</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">Allah is:</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1; padding-left: 18px\">\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">The Most Merciful \ud83e\udd0d</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">The Most Forgiving</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">The Most Just \u2696</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">The Provider \ud83c\udf27</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">The Creator \ud83c\udf31</li></ul>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">If there was no creation:</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1; padding-left: 18px\">\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">How would mercy be shown?</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">How would forgiveness exist?</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">How would justice appear?</li></ul>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">Creation allows His qualities to be seen.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">\ud83c\udf3f </span><span style=\" font-size:12pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">4\ufe0f\u20e3 Humans Are Special</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">Humans were given:</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1; padding-left: 18px\">\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Intelligence \ud83e\udde0</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Free will</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Moral responsibility</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Ability to know right and wrong</li></ul>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">Angels do not disobey.<br />Animals follow instinct.<br />Humans can choose.</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">That choice makes us special.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">\u2696 </span><span style=\" font-size:12pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">5\ufe0f\u20e3 This World Is Temporary</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">This life is short.<br />It is not the final destination.</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">The real life is the Hereafter.</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">This world is like:</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1; padding-left: 18px\">\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">An exam hall \ud83d\udcdd</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">A training ground</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">A preparation stage</li></ul>\n<hr />\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">\ud83d\udca1 </span><span style=\" font-size:12pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">Simple Example</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">Imagine a company:</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1; padding-left: 18px\">\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Owner creates factory.</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Hires workers.</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Gives instructions.</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Tests performance.</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Then gives salary.</li></ul>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">This world is like that system.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">\ud83c\udf1f </span><span style=\" font-size:12pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;\">Simple Clear Answer</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">Allah created the world and humans:</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">\ud83d\udc49 To worship Him<br />\ud83d\udc49 To test us<br />\ud83d\udc49 To show His wisdom and mercy<br />\ud83d\udc49 To give us chance for eternal reward</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">Now think deeply \ud83e\udd14</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">If this world was created only for enjoyment\u2026<br />Why is there death?<br />Why is there justice after life?</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">If you want, next we can go even deeper:</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1; padding-left: 18px\">\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Why did Allah create us if He already knows everything? \ud83c\udf3f</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; -qt-block-indent: 0; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px\">Or why is there suffering in the world? \ud83d\udcad</li></ul></body></html>",
